snippet.title: Final Destination Bloodlines | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Death is a relentless son of a *****. #FinalDestination #Bloodlines - Only in Theaters and IMAX May 16. #FilmedforIMAX

The newest chapter in New Line Cinema’s bloody successful franchise takes audiences back to the very beginning of Death’s twisted sense of justice—“Final Destination Bloodlines.”  

Plagued by a violent recurring nightmare, college student Stefanie heads home to track down the one person who might be able to break the cycle and save her family from the grisly demise that inevitably awaits them all. 
“Final Destination Bloodlines” stars Kaitlyn Santa Juana, Teo Briones, Richard Harmon, Owen Patrick Joyner, Anna Lore, with Brec Bassinger, and Tony Todd.

The film is directed by Adam Stein & Zach Lipovsky. The screenplay is by Guy Busick & Lori Evans Taylor, and story is by Jon Watts and Guy Busick & Lori Evans Taylor. It is based on characters created by Jeffrey Reddick.
“Final Destination Bloodlines” is produced by Craig Perry, Sheila Hanahan Taylor, Jon Watts, Dianne McGunigle and Toby Emmerich. The executive producers are David Siegel and Warren Zide. The behind-the-camera talent includes director of photography Christian Sebaldt and production designer Rachel O’Toole. The film is edited by Sabrina Pitre. The music is by Tim Wynn. The costumes are designed by Michelle Hunter. The casting is by Rich Delia.

New Line Cinema presents A Practical Pictures / Freshman Year / Fireside Films Production: “Final Destination Bloodlines.” The film will be distributed in theaters and IMAX worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on May 16, 2025, and internationally beginning on 14 May 2025.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | HOLO LOLO | Shankuraj Konwar X Shalmali Kholgade
snippet.description:
Across cultures, resilience and wisdom are often passed down through generations, shaping how we navigate adulthood. Inspired by the famed Moran community, #HoloLolo is a soulful track performed by Assam local #shankurajkonwar, as he tells the story of the challenges of navigating adulthood along with #shalmalikholgade, who brings her unique perspective. A variety of cultural instruments - namely the toka, gogona, and siphung, play an integral role in the composition, bringing alive the sounds of Assam, elevated with supporting electronic soundscapes.

Listen to HOLO LOLO - http://umgindia.lnk.to/HoloLolo

CREDITS

Composition: Shankuraj Konwar
Singers: Shankuraj Konwar, Shalmali Kholgade

Folk composition: Sarat Moran
Lyrics: Himanshu Sutiya Saikia (Assamese) & Shloke Lal (Hindi)

Music Production & Sound Design: Ishan Das
Music Arrangement: Ishan Das, Shankuraj Konwar

Aas Paas Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 25th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

snippet.title: #VT15 Shoot Begins | Varun Tej | Merlapaka Gandhi | Thaman S | Satya | Ritika Nayak | UV Creations
snippet.description:
VT15 Shoot Begins Video on UV Creations.

Mega Prince Varun Tej’s upcoming film VT15 is an upcoming INDO KOREAN HORROR COMEDY FILM, written and directed by Merlapaka Gandhi. Mann Mast Malang Episode 16 Teaser - 23rd March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.title: Train -The Unforgettable Journey | Stand up Comedy By Harsh Gujral
snippet.description:
This video is a satirical take on incidents that even Men have to go through in our day to day lives. I have tried to convey a simple message that Men's Safety is never been talked about in this country but deserves equal attention and solutions. Train The Unforgettable Journey has all my experiences and problems i have faced while travelling in a public transport in a funny manner. Please watch the video share with your friends so that there is a message spread in a funny way.
Thank You.

Episode 4354: Jethalal Gets Stuck In The Car
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal lands in trouble when his co-passenger suddenly escapes, leaving him stranded in the car. Meanwhile, Bagha and Nattu Kaka eagerly wait for him. Will he make it on time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4354 | 25 Mar 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Prema Velluva - Lyrical | HIT 3 | Nani | Sailesh Kolanu | Srinidhi Shetty | Mickey J Meyer
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the first single ''Prema Velluva'' from ''HIT 3'' starring Nani and Srinidhi Shetty. Directed by Dr. Sailesh Kolanu. Music Composed by Mickey J Meyer. Sung by Sid Sriram and Nutana Mohan. 

Song Credits:
Singers: Sid Sriram, Nutana Mohan
Lyrics: Krishna Kanth
Music: Mickey J Meyer
Choreography: Vishwa Raghu
Costume Designer: Nani Kamarsu
Stills: Sridhar Chadalawada
Keyboards: Mickey J Meyer
Rhythm: Venkatesh Patvari
Bass: Neil
Song Mixed by: Mickey J Meyer
Song Mastered by: Darren Vermaas (NY)
Music Recording Studio: Inspire Studio (California, Hyderabad)

Cast & Crew Details:
Starring 'Natural Star' as 'Arjun Sarkaar'.
Writer & Director : Dr. Sailesh Kolanu
Producer : Prashanti Tipirneni
Banners : Wall Poster Cinema & Unanimous Productions
Music : Mickey J Meyer
Cinematography : Sanu John Varghese
Editor : Karthika Srinivas R
Production Designer : Sri Nagendra Tangala
Executive Producer : S Venkatratnam (Venkat)
Sound design : Sync Cinema
PRO : Vamsi Shekar
Marketing : First Show
Publicity Designs : Aesthetic Kunjamma

Lyrics:

Dhuke naapai ila 
Ivvale ye ye 
Prema velluvaa

Pallavi 1:
Pagale naa vaipuki nadiche kalavaa 
Paduthuu yegire alavaa
Manase ninu chudani okate godava 
Kanule ipude chadhivaa
Venta vacchave Vembadinchaave 
Oopiralle maarave nede neeve
Nammi theerale kala kaadhe 
Peruke nenunnale praanam neeve
Yevarevarani vethikina Kanulaki thanu dhorikenaa 
Marichaanika dheninainaa nee valana
 
Pallavi 2:
Telusa tholisaariga 
Manase gelichaa 
Yepudu yedhute nilichaa
Kopam marichaanugaa Idi nee mahimaa?
Nijame nuvu naa sagamaa?

Chorus:
Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Charanam:
Ato ito yetainaa
Aduge jarige mela mellagaa Marintha 
okatokatiga cherenaa 
Manalo maname kalise vidhama
Geetha geesane vechi choosane
Ninnu minchi naakinka thodantu dhorukunaa
Aapalenule aagalenule Choopalenule cheppalenule
Dhaachalenu neninkaa naalo preema
Yevarevarani vethikina Kanulaki thanu dhorikena 
Marichaanika dheninainaa nee valana

Chorus:
Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

snippet.title: Aas Paas Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 22nd March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 22nd March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:
Ali Ansari as Dr. Saham
Laiba Khan as Arshia/Arshi
Samina Ahmed as Aneeqa Begum
Saba Faisal as Seemab
Saife Hasan as Kamal
Sahiba Afzal as Kashifa
Afzal Khan (Jan Rambo) as Ausaf 
Namra Shahid as Shagoofa 
Fahima Awan as Aneela
Faisal Naqvi as Musheer
Alina Chaudhry as Aneela's Mother-in-law 
Nain Sukh as Anooshia/Anooshi
Ahsan Afzal Khan as Ammad
Ahmed Usman as Shehroze

snippet.title: Officer Purvi ने किया Culprit को Trace | CID | सी.आई.डी.| Latest Episode | 24 Mar 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

A famous kabaddi player named Vishal dies in the middle of a Kabaddi national level tournament. His friend Deepali confesses that she gave his contract to a contract killer. Players from the opposite teams are suspects but Dr Salunkhe has some shocking revelations about the death. How did Vishal die? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1129
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #cid2025 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:
Haseena को जब Cheetah ने बताया की Karishma Singh चंद दिनों की मेहमान है | Maddam Sir | Hindi Comedy Show | Full Episode

Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humour of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences which add to the drama and comedy.

snippet.title: March Update is HERE! | Clash On!
snippet.description:
March Update is upon us! Featuring MC Sneezy and Lil’ Furnace. Find out what’s to come from them directly. For more details on what's new in this update, visit https://supercell.com/en/games/clashofclans/blog/release-notes/welcome-to-clash-anytime-update/

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

#clashofclans

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Vehem | રાકેશ બારોટ | વ્હેમ | Navu Gujarati Bewafa Geet 2025
snippet.description:
Rakesh Barot new bewafa song “Vehem” is a soulful Gujarati song by Rakesh Barot, expressing the pain of betrayal and heartbreak. This track captures deep emotions through its powerful lyrics and Barot's heartfelt vocals, offering a fresh take on the theme of unfaithfulness in relationships. Watch now only on @SaregamaGujarati

Lyrics:
તારી હારે પ્રેમ કરી હૂતો પછતાણો 
હો.... તારી હારે પ્રેમ કરી હૂતો પછતાણો,
ખોટી તારી વાતો માં હું તો ભરમાણો.
તું કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારો વેમ (2)
સુ ખામી હતી કેને મારા રે પ્રેમ માં, 
વોંધો પડ્યો અલી કઈ મારી વાત માં કઈ મારી વાત માં.....
હો.. બળજબરી થી મે પ્રેમ નોતો કર્યો, 
આપી વિશ્વાસ તે સાથ મારો છોડ્યો 
તું કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારો વેમ (2)
હો..હો..ગરજ હતી ત્યારે મીઠું મીઠું બોલતી, 
રોજ રોજ ફોન કરી મળવા બોલાવતી 
હો..હો...હો ખોટું ખોટું બોલી મોટા સપના બતાવતી, 
સાથ મારો છોડી તે તો રંગ રે બતાયો 
હૂતો તારી વાતો માં કેવો રે ફસાણો,
કોને કૌ હૂતો કેવો હલવાનો કેવો હલવાનો....
અરે હાચા મારા પ્રેમ ને ભૂલી રે ગઈ, 
કિનારે લાવી ને મને ડુબાડી ગઈ....
એ કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારી વેમ 
કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારી વેમ 
હો... કસમો ખાધેલી તે મારા પ્રેમ ની, 
તારા વિના જાનું મારી જિંદગી નકામી. 
હો.....મે તો માનીતી અલી તને રે પોતાની,
તું તો નીકળી હાવ ખોટી રે દગાળી. 
અરે પ્રેમ પ્રેમ કોઈ નથી ખોટી મગજમારી, 
મારી ભૂલ મને હવે હમજાણી હવે હમજાણી....
અરે જરૂજ તને નથી તો ગરજ મને નથી, 
હાચા મારા પ્રેમ ની કદર તને નથી 
તું કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારો વેમ 
કરતી હતી પ્રેમ એ હતો મારો વેમ (2)

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 21st March 2025
snippet.description:

snippet.title: NZ vs PAK 3rd T20I - Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand 2025 | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
In the 3rd T20I of Pakistan’s Tour of New Zealand, Hasan Nawaz smashed a blistering 44-ball century to guide Pakistan to a 9-wicket win in Auckland. Chasing down 205 in just 16 overs, Nawaz’s explosive knock led Pakistan to victory. Earlier, Mohammad Haris contributed a quickfire 41 off 20 balls. Mark Chapman’s 94 helped New Zealand post 204. Watch the thrilling highlights as Pakistan aims to keep their T20I series hopes alive under new captain Salman Ali Agha.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Empuraan Hyderabad Pressmeet  | Mohanlal | Prithviraj Sukumaran | Sujith Vasudev
snippet.description:
Empuraan Hyderabad Pressmeet  | Mohanlal | Prithviraj Sukumaran | Sujith Vasudev 

#empuraan #empuraanupdate #mohanlal #mohanlalfans #prithvirajsukumaran #manjuwarrier #muraligopy #indrajithsukumaran 

L2: Empuraan also called L2E, is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language action thriller film directed by Prithviraj Sukumaran, written by Murali Gopy and jointly produced by Lyca Productions and Aashirvad Cinemas. It is the second instalment in a planned trilogy, following the 2019 film Lucifer. The film stars Mohanlal as Khureshi-Ab'raam / Stephen Nedumpally, alongside Prithviraj Sukumaran, Tovino Thomas, Indrajith Sukumaran, Manju Warrier, Saniya Iyappan, Saikumar, Baiju Santhosh, Fazil and Sachin Khedekar reprising their roles from the original.

Lucifer was always intended to be a series from its inception, originally conceived as a three-part film. The first part was made into the film Lucifer. The success of the first film led to the decision to proceed with the second instalment in the series. Murali took the opportunity to expand the scale and scope of Empuraan. The screenplay was finalised in July 2022, and pre-production began the following month. Lyca Productions joined as a producer in 2023, marking their debut in Malayalam, alongside Aashirvad Cinemas, the producer of the original. The film's music was composed by Deepak Dev.

snippet.title: 3 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN
snippet.description:
3 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN. You asked for it. The return of Minecraft Manhunt, George, Sapnap and Dream VS a real life Titan.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

George:  @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

All video music is custom scored and produced by Dream & PmBata. 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt 2: TITAN TAKEDOWN. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is a massive, near invincible TITAN, being controlled by a real life human projected into the game using our custom fusion technology, 3D cameras, and a VR headset. This is the toughest challenge I have faced yet. GeorgeNotFound, Sapnap and I are on a team of 3, and are trying to speedrun and beat the game before we die to the titan.

If someone dies, they cannot respawn. If I die, the challenge is over. The titan's compass points to me at all times.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my anonymous friend tries everything he can to stop me. This is all custom coded by us. 

If this video gets 1,000,000 likes we'll make my next video another one :)

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt #TitanTakedown

snippet.title: गुढीपाडवा स्पेशल थाळी | घरच्या किचनमध्ये नेवैद्य - अळूवडी, बासुंदी, पुरी,मसाले भात Gudhipadva Recipe
snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - https://www.amazon.in/s?me=A6FSX0SQK7GV6&marketplaceID=A21TJRUUN4KGV

गुढीपाडवा स्पेशल थाळी | घरच्या किचनमध्ये नेवैद्य - अळूवडी, बासुंदी, पुरी,मसाले भात Gudhipadva Recipe स्वामी समर्थ प्रकट दिन विशेष / गुढीपाडवा विशेष संपूर्ण थाळी |
बासुंदी रेसिपी पुरी, तोंडली भात, बटाटा भाजी, अळूची वडी, कैरीची डाळ, कुरडई

पुरी रेसिपी | Puri Recipe
गव्हाचे पीठ २ कप | Wheat Flour 2 cups
बारीक रवा २ चमचे | Semolina 2 tbsp
मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
साखर १/२ टीस्पून | Sugar ½ tsp
तेल २ चमचे | Oil 2 tsp
पाणी पीठ भिजवण्यासाठी | Water to knead the dough

तोंडली भात रेसिपी |मसाले भात रेसिपी | Masala Bhaat Recipe in marathi
तांदूळ २ वाटी |Rice 2 cups
तेल २ टेबलस्पून |Oil 2-3 tbsp
मोहरी पाव टीस्पून | Mustard seeds ¼ tsp
जिरे पाव टीस्पून | Cumin ¼ tsp
हिंग पाव टीस्पून | Hing ¼ tsp
कढीपत्ता | Curry leaves
दालचिनी १ | Cinnamon 1 
तमालपत्र २ | Bay leaves 2
मिरे ४-५ | Black pepper corns 4-5
लवंग ४-५ | Cloves 4-5
वेलदोडे २-३ | Green Cardamom 2-3
काजूच्या पाकळ्या १०-१२ | Cashews 10-12
उभ्या चिरलेल्या हिरव्या मिरच्या १-२ | Slit Green chilies 1-2 
उभी पातळ चिरलेली तोंडली १०० ग्राम | Sliced Tondali (pointed gourd) 100 gms
मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
हळद १/४ टीस्पून | Turmeric ¼ tsp
मिरची पावडर १/२ टीस्पून | Red chilly pw ½ tsp
गोडा मसाला २ टीस्पून | Goda Masala 2 tsp
चिरलेली कोथिंबीर थोडी | Chopped Fresch Coriander
धुतलेले तांदूळ | Washed Rice 
गरम पाणी ४ वाटी | Hot Water 4 Cups
मीठ गरजेनुसार | Salt to taste
ओल्या नारळाचा चव २ टेबलस्पून | Scraped fresh coconut 2 tbsp
वरून पेरण्यासाठी कोथिंबीर व थोडा ओल्या नारळाचा चव | Chopped fresh coriander & fresh coconut scraped for garnishint
साजूक तूप | Ghee for serving

बटाटा भाजी रेसिपी | Alu ki sabji recipe / bhandare wali alu ki sabji
बटाटे ४०० ग्राम | Boiled potatoes 400 gms
वाटण - For Watan
टोमॅटो २ मोठे | Tomatoes 2 large
हिरवी मिरची २-३ | Green chilies 2-3
आले २ इंच | Ginger 2 inch 
मसाला साठी | For masala 
जिरे १ टीस्पून | Cumin 1 tsp
काली मिरी १०-१२ | Black pepper corns 10-12
बडीशेप १ टीस्पून | Fennel seeds 1 tsp
फोडणी | Fodani
तेल ४ चमचे | Oil 4 tbsp
जिरे १/२ टीस्पून | Cumin ½ tsp
हिंग १/४ टीस्पून | Hing ¼ tsp
हळद १/२ टीस्पून | Turmeric ½ tsp
काश्मिरी मिरची पावडर १ टीस्पून | Kashmiri chily pw 1 tsp
तयार पेस्ट | ready paste
उकडलेले बटाटे | boiled potatoes
गरम पाणी | hot water
धने पूड १ टीस्पून | coriander pw 
गरम मसाला पावडर १ टीस्पून | garam masala 1 tsp
हिरव्या मिरच्या | Slit green chilies 3-4

snippet.title: Jetha क्यों घूम रहा है Chips के Packets के साथ? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Scenes
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Despite their best efforts, Taarak and Jetha are unable to get tea wherever they go, which prevents them from finding some peace and quiet.  They get at Popatlal's house and discover that he is out of milk to make tea, so they go in despair.  They then locate a tiny tea stall where they must buy numerous packages of chips in order to get change.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1862
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #comedyscene #tmkocbestcomedy 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Scenes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS8wi0cuF6h1ZN4wQuXjH2m

Kallu rendu pusthakaalu
Bhasha leni aksharaalu

Leniponi kaaranaalu

Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le

Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu

Oohallo untunte praanaalu

Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..
